\ip N…ôkuku…ô i kani m…ô Fas Korin Pol r…®m…ôrai rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe Korin ia nuk 55. Pol ramar…ô fwe Efesas m…ôrhi pen n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe Korin t…® n…®r…®pwenien n…ôkuku…ô s…ôv…ônraha. Korin ram…ômak ia n…®kare t…ôsi Metiterenian. In taon asori riti. S…ôv…ônhi naut…ô rasori. M…ôt…ô noien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Korin r…ôr…ôha. Ia t…ôn…ômt…ôn…ô me pam n…ôrmama h…ôukur…ôn m…ô Korin in taon …ôr…ôha riti. T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô nakalasia me fwe Korin h…ôuvehe vi a mhahat…ôt…ô ia Iesu Kristo, r…ôknek…®n t…® nir…ôha t…® noien noien amasan. Ir…ôha kamho ihi noien …ôr…ôha. Nakalasia me fwe Korin ham…ôvis…ô m…®nraha me. Ir…ôha nepw…®n kamho noien …ôr…ôha anan. Pol r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô…°kiari skai m…®nraha mamahat…ôn ir…ôha m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôfar…ô ir…ô. In r…®rai n…ô…°kiariien me nepw…®n ia n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô trahat…ôn ir…ôha ia nar…ôien s…ôv…ônraha. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô ir…ôha hesi pen n…ô…°kiariien me n…ôha n…ôn…ô tuh…ôukur…ôn noien amasan m…®ne noien …ôr…ôha.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Iou Pol, iou aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®no r…ômwhen ia s…ô in rokeikei, m…ôkwein iou m…ô tako wok i, m…®ne pi…ôvtaha Sostenes.
