\v 30 \x - \xo 1:30 \xt Jer 23:5-6, Jon 17:19, 2Kor 5:21\x*M…ôt…ô in r…®no k…®miaha hi…ôuvehe mho kuatia k…®miaha Iesu Kristo. N…ôn…ô Kristo in nukur…ônien s…ôk…®taha ruku pen t…® Kumwes…ôn. In r…®no k…®taha s…ôuvehe mhatukwatukw ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn. In r…®no k…®taha s…ôuvehe mho n…ôkur ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi. In r…®n…ôr…ôku suatuk m…®fi raka nari ia k…®taha.
